---
title: BPMN-style flow — Outbox Reconciliation (Spec §10.2)
---
flowchart LR
    start([⏱ Cron */10 min]):::evt
    backlog{COUNT undispatched > 1000?}:::gw
    alert[Emit OutboxBacklogHigh<br/>Grafana alert]:::task
    fetch[SELECT outbox_events<br/>WHERE published_at IS NULL<br/>AND created_at < now()-1min<br/>AND attempts < 10]:::task
    each{rows?}:::gw
    pub[PUBLISH to Redis ws.broadcast]:::task
    ok[UPDATE published_at, attempts++]:::task
    failBranch{attempts >= 10?}:::gw
    poison[Mark poison-pill<br/>attempts = 99]:::task
    log[Increment outbox_poison_total]:::task
    done([✅ End]):::evt

    start --> backlog
    backlog -->|yes| alert --> fetch
    backlog -->|no| fetch
    fetch --> each
    each -->|no| done
    each -->|yes| pub
    pub -->|success| ok --> each
    pub -->|exception| failBranch
    failBranch -->|yes| poison --> log --> each
    failBranch -->|no| each

    classDef evt fill:#fff5d6,stroke:#b58900;
    classDef task fill:#e0f0ff,stroke:#268bd2;
    classDef gw fill:#f0e0ff,stroke:#6c71c4;
